               <msContents>
                  <summary>Ziq Chants, መጽሐፈ፡ ዚቅ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="221r" facs="003">Fols 1r–221r</locus>
                      <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1979Mashaf">Maṣḥafa ziq</title>
                      <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                      <incipit xml:lang="gez">በ፩ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ብፁዕ፡ አንተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ዘሀለወከ፡ ታእምር፡ ወተሐውር፡ ቅድመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                      <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus from="1r" facs="003">Fols 1r and following</locus>
                        <foreign xml:lang="gez">በኃይለ፡ እዚአብሔር፡ ተወጥነ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዚቅ፡ ዘአስተጋብዕዎ፡ ሊቃውንት፡ ኅሩያን፡ በ፲፪ወ፱፻፡ ፷ወ፫፡ ዓመት፡ አሜን።</foreign>
                      </colophon>
                      <notatedMusic><desc>With musical notation</desc></notatedMusic>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
